9 AN ACT TO AMEND PROVISIONS OF THE ARKANSAS CODE
10 CONCERNING TEACHER INCENTIVE AND MERIT PAY; TO AMEND
11 REQUIREMENTS CONCERNING SUMMATIVE EVALUATIONS UNDER
12 THE TEACHER EXCELLENCE AND SUPPORT SYSTEM; TO AMEND
13 PUBLIC SCHOOL DISTRICT REQUIREMENTS UNDER THE MERIT
14 TEACHER INCENTIVE FUND PROGRAM; AND FOR OTHER
15 PURPOSES.
