17
Subtitle
18
19 TO AMEND ELIGIBILITY FOR TEACHER
20 INCENTIVE AND MERIT PAY; TO AMEND
21 REQUIREMENTS FOR SUMMATIVE EVALUATIONS;
22 AND TO AMEND SCHOOL DISTRICT
23 REQUIREMENTS UNDER THE MERIT TEACHER
24 INCENTIVE FUND PROGRAM.
25
26 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF ARKANSAS:
27
28 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code § 6-17-413, concerning yearly incentive
29 bonuses for certain teachers with National Board for Professional Teaching
30 Standards certification funding, is amended to add an additional subsection
31 to read as follows:
32 (g) A person shall not be qualified to receive funds under this
33 section if he or she has not satisfied the requirements of this section by
34 July 1, 2025.
35
36 SECTION 2. Arkansas Code § 6-17-2805(c), concerning summative
